{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think you have a few pieces that you saw of rabbis and things, probably, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They say about, you know, what-- but I can do nothing anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had there about 10 Russian people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were in the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these are the ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with one Greek guy, [INAUDIBLE] Baruch, that they put together, you know, a scheme how to be able to make a revolt in the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is what I know, that they, they were in Block 2 first, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put the scheme.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that Greek guy was a captain in the Greek army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they-- but we didn't-- they-- they put a date for the revolution, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think it was 19 of October.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have all the-- and it didn't happen because the first one was because of the-- were the people on the-- on the thing, they were on the-- I don't know, I can't remember the name of the place.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were-- they were outside-- the Germans were [INAUDIBLE] keeping the-- an eye on the-- on the-- on the camp, and they-- they couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Something happens, and we abandoned that date of revolution.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they put a newer [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the only thing I-- I know, I think I-- you can read it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You'll find out exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because what they-- we saw is that 1:30 in the morning one day, we see flames coming from crematorium 3.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we were in crematorium 2 always ready to-- to be part of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so-- but the-- the-- the Polish guy that were in our number 2 didn't let us do anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
